            <title>[PIG-3591] Refactor POPackage to separate MR specific code from packaging</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3591</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;POPackage is currently closely associated with the MR shuffle semantics. This makes it difficult to adapt the variety of subclasses of POPackage to other execution engines without duplicating code.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
